rows.label: bf11020100_0020
rows.name: And it's not just the Volff and Feris...

rows.label: bf11020100_0030
rows.name:
Why are the Urus attacking?
They're usually so peaceful.

rows.label: bf11020100_0060
rows.name: So that's what that stench is...

rows.label: bf11020100_0070
rows.name:
Yes. No doubt about it.
It's the scent of blood.

rows.label: bf11020100_0080
rows.name: It's driving them into a frenzy.
